charlmap <- addTiles(leaflet())
addCircleMarkers(setView(charlmap, lng=-80.84, lat=35.22,zoom = 13), 
                 lng = charlotte_rests$longitude, lat = charlotte_rests$latitude, radius = 1, 
                 fillOpacity = 3, color = "blue")
top10map <- addTiles(leaflet())
addCircleMarkers(setView(top10map, lng=-80.84, lat=35.22,zoom = 11), 
                 lng = top10rated$longitude, lat = top10rated$latitude, radius = 4, 
                 fillOpacity = 3, color = "green")
